properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 11 at 1:55PM EST until January 12 at 10:00AM EST by NWS State College PA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Wind gusts from the southwest 45 to 50 mph expected.

* WHERE...Sullivan County.

* WHEN...From 3 AM to 10 AM EST Sunday.

* IMPACTS...Gusty winds could blow around unsecured objects. Tree
limbs could be blown down and a few power outages may result.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

For high wind safety information, visit weather.gov/wind.

The latest forecast information can be found on the
NWS State College Facebook page and Twitter @NWSStateCollege,
or on the web at weather.gov/ctp.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 3 AM TO 10 AM EST SUNDAY
